related_questions.snippet: Jobcentre. The centre of jobs. ... The first thing to know is that you don't have to be claiming Jobseeker's Allowance to use the jobcentre. related_questions.question: Can you go to the Jobcentre without an appointment?
related_questions.snippet: It is possible to go into your local Jobcentre Plus and make an appointment with an advisor who will help you through everything you need to know about benefits. ...
